      Welcome to the United States District Court for the Eastern District of
      Louisiana. We are authorized 12 Active Judges, have 9 Senior Judges and
      6 Magistrate Judges.

      The court does not accept documents submitted for filing by email or
      fax.  If you have comments or suggestions, you may either use our
   Feedback Form or contact us by mail/email/fax/telephone.
